00:59:17,787 --> 00:59:18,621
but they are not.

1036
00:59:18,621 --> 00:59:20,356
- I know, I know.

1037
00:59:20,356 --> 00:59:21,858
Oh my God, he showed up.

1038
00:59:21,858 --> 00:59:22,692
Hi.

1039
00:59:23,993 --> 00:59:25,261
They're not gonna sit
 with us, are they?

1040
00:59:25,261 --> 00:59:28,164
- No, they're not
  gonna sit with us.

